import xarray as xr
import numpy as np
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
%matplotlib widget

def tohours(Time):
    return np.unwrap(Time.values.astype('float') / 1e9 /3600, period=296 * 24 * 30 * 12 )

with xr.open_dataset('Overturning.snapshot.nc') as ds:
    display(ds)
    fig, axs = plt.subplots(1, 2)
    sst = 16 - 12 * np.cos((60*40e3 - ds.yt*1000) * np.pi / 60 / 40e3)
    axs[0].plot(ds.yt, sst)
